RStudio CRAN mirror

Aggregated server logs of the RStudio CRAN mirror are publicly available. The provided data is likely not really representative for R users as I expect that only package installations/updates via the RStudio IDEs are covered. However, logs of other CRAN mirrors are AFAIK not publicly available.

Version statistics

Operating System statistics

I expect that the OS-dependent data may be quite distorted: Id expect that installations on servers a) more frequently use Linux/Unix systems which b) install/update via closeby CRAN mirrors rather than the RStudio CRAN mirror. On the other hand, download statistics anyways underestimate the number of users for server systems.

In any case, the vast majority of hyperSpec users downloading via the RStudio CRAN mirror works on Windows.
